ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR PROPRIETARY API INTEGRATION:

This software is designed to work with ioSystems' proprietary AI chat API.
While this widget code is open source under the MIT License, the following
additional terms apply when using it with ioSystems' proprietary services:

1. API Access: Access to ioSystems' AI chat API requires a valid site token
   and may be subject to separate terms of service and usage limits.

2. Data Processing: When using this widget with ioSystems' API, user messages
   and data are processed according to ioSystems' privacy policy and terms
   of service for the proprietary API service.

3. Commercial Use: While the widget code is open source, commercial use of
   the integrated service may require appropriate licensing agreements with
   ioSystems.

4. Support: Support for the widget itself is provided under open source
   terms, but API-related issues are subject to ioSystems' proprietary
   service support agreements.

For questions about API licensing and commercial use, please contact:
legal@iosystems.com

For open source issues and contributions, please visit:
https://github.com/iosystems/chat-widget

